{"tid":1420802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好忘記11月左右有一件好重要嘅事要儘快阻止","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:55.000Z","uid":156861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"31d5a2f64a8cdfd1f8b7c9f347475284d978dc45","tid":1420802,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"唔知有幾多人見到，見到嘅可以推一推嘅<br />\n<br />\n11月就係軍政府盧大帥榮休之日<br />\n<br />\n鄧副帥將會如無意外坐上大帥之位<br />\n<br />\n大家應該知道鄧副處長過去手段強硬嘅業績<br />\n<br />\n加上我地嘅抗爭如無意外係長期作戰<br />\n<br />\n除咗五大訴求外真係要諗盡方法拉鄧炳強落馬<br />\n<br />\n煲大元朗警黑事件等等各種方法要用盡佢<br />\n<br />\n否則即使文宣等等各種手法我地撐到去十一月但<br />\n<br />\n佢一上件我地各單位嘅手足(唔止勇武)多個月隨時一舖清袋<br />\n<br />\nsor for 1999"},{"pid":"a4f9f7b54ee9f92e54c24cd2cd7e4048c6205e3b","tid":1420802,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efa866d723802bda58c1c5530bda9db02e281eec","tid":1420802,"uid":253833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88b9c913552d40606e68382f82838b48d01c4745","tid":1420802,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa866d723802bda58c1c5530bda9db02e281eec","tid":1420802,"uid":253833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:52.000Z","msg":"［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37bc4382639e82ff0bd1d471abb85217252f2cbf","tid":1420802,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"不得不推"},{"pid":"5e98e12040751719e1f3f132004dde5b529dea78","tid":1420802,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime